comments: Griffin (DET) makes contact to the arm of Nurkic (POR) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Lillard (POR) wraps Griffin (DET) after the dribble handoff.
Nurkic (POR) cleanly deflects the basketball on Drummond's (DET) shot attempt.
Kennard (DET) makes contact to the body of Lillard (POR) after the release that affects his ability to  follow through safely.
Kennard (DET) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Aminu (POR) while setting the pick.
Nurkic (POR) makes marginal contact with Galloway (DET) as he rolls to the basket after the pick.
Drummond (DET) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Aminu (POR) and briefly extends his arms while the two disengage.
Griffin (DET) makes contact to Nurkic's (POR) body that affects his SQBR.
The Trail Blazers commit a 24 second violation.
Galloway (DET) briefly places a hand/arm to the front of Lillard (POR) during the drive.
Galloway (DET) maintains a legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Lillard's (POR) shot attempt.
Drummond (DET) and Aminu (POR) make marginal contact with one another during the inbound.
Lillard (DET) and Kennard (DET) make incidental foot to foot contact prior to the inbound pass.
Drummond (DET) moves into and delivers contact to Curry (POR) that affects his defensive position.
